<idea-plugin>
    <id>top.zhoukunqiang.sql.parser</id>
    <name>Sql parser</name>
    <version>1.1.0</version>
    <vendor email="imzhoukunqiang@gmail.com" url="https://www.zhoukunqiang.top">zhoukunqiang</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
      Mybatis sql转换器，可以将mybatis控制台输出的语句和参数转化为普通sql语句，方便执行。<br>
      使用方法：选中需要转换的sql和参数，右键，点击Parse to sql即可。
    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[

            优化SQL参数获取方式，修复部分参数获取错误的BUG.
        <br>
            修复因空格导致SQL无法获取的问题。
        <br>
            修复因参数后缀有空格失效的情况
        <br>
            2020-06-23 增加sql格式化功能
    ]]>
    </change-notes>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/build_number_ranges.html for description -->
    <idea-version since-build="182"/>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <!-- uncomment to enable plugin in all products
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    -->

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->

    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <!-- Add your actions here -->
        <group id="SqlParser.Group">

            <add-to-group group-id="ConsoleEditorPopupMenu" relative-to-action="CompareClipboardWithSelection"
                          anchor="before"/>
            <separator/>
            <action id="SqlParser.SetSql" class="com.github.imzhoukunqiang.parser.action.SqlParseAction" text="Parse to Sql"/>
        </group>
    </actions>

</idea-plugin>